Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:48.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:48.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:52.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:52.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:58.66,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly the flag, Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:58.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,hata wo ageyou Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:04.66,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make waves, jump from your sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:04.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,namikaze tateyou suriipu kara no janpusutaato
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:09.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:09.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:13.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,your toughness, that’s what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:13.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no tafunesu sore ga hitsuyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:16.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,medachisugi sorette tsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:16.88,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:19.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:19.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted->means Winner:D
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jiyuu dakega ore tachi no ruuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.93,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is our only rule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:30.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinpai nante dokofuku kaze--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:30.90,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our way to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:33.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ttai one piece ichibannori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:33.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:37.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:37.53,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:41.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:41.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s important not to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:44.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:44.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:48.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:48.75,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:52.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:52.59,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:59.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:59.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:02.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:02.76,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:07.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:07.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:14.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:14.23,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:18.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:18.65,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:21.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:21.32,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:25.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:25.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.58,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:39.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:39.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, \Nthe second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,turned to rubber after \Nhe ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the New Fish-Man Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who are looking to destroy \Nthe Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...assisted by Vander Decken, \Nwho is after Shirahoshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats find themselves\N caught up in the turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I join the Warlords,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aladdin and the others who \Ndon't want to be pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.62,0:04:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can live in this country \Nwithout being chased
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,under the amnesty of the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go our own way, just like we used to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sun Pirates split into three groups
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and went separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shaking Fish-Man Island! A \NCelestial Dragon Drifts In!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:36.67,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE FISH-MAN ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't believe that this day has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were the Celestial Dragons' slaves,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we were hopeless and all we \Nhad was hatred toward them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got away from the Celestial \NDragons thanks to Boss Tai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but still they were looking for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:05:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought being a pirate was \Nthe only way to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now we can even go back to \Nour hometown without hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are free!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! No, Brother Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget what you've done for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't, but we know what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You needed the amnesty of the \NGovernment to help free us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you joined the Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as though you wanted to join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit this chatting and go \Nto your family already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! They're becoming impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Honey...\N--Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Baby...\N--Just go to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dad!\N--Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aladdin, you were a slave just like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now you can get off of the ship finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will no longer be chased \Nas renegade slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of us can stay with family without fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just like the mark \Nof the Celestial Dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because of our terrible experience as \Nslaves, our hatred toward humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will never go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I understand what \NBrother Tai truly meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that Boss Jimbei
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is becoming a tool of the \NWorld Government... or humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he forget who killed Tiger-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost respect for Boss Jimbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that there were many islanders
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who didn't like the idea \Nof me joining the Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:08.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE RYUGU PALACE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Jimbei's momentous decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.19,0:07:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now we have a relationship \Nwith the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to use this opportunity to \Nestablish friendly relations with humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will keep trying hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if it's for his friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Jimbei took \Non such a big burden-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he gets an order from \Nthe World Government,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he has no choice but to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...whether he likes it or not-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will put himself in \Nharm's way and occasionally
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his blood will be spilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let Jimbei's sacrifice end up wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do my best, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want you to \Nsuffer another hangover-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then something happened that would
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,change Queen Otohime's life forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An uninvited visitor came to the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryugu Kingdom! Ryugu Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is border patrol speaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge wrecked ship is seeking \Nemergency entry into the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you waiting for?! \NAccept them already...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Celestial Dragon is on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Celestial Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accept them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Send a rescue team immediately!\N--Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll meet them myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is a Celestial Dragon \Ndoing on the seafloor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Celestial Dragon's ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must've been attacked by \Nsome deep-sea creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look down on us Fish-Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come they were in such deep water?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! They are all dead! What weaklings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me a breathing mask now, you fishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:26.06,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,A WORLD NOBLE (CELESTIAL \NDRAGON) SAINT MYOSGARD
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand this Fish-man's smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me a mask now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and save my life, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has no respect of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how you ask somebody to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is a medical team here?\N--They're here but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they don't know what to do with "it."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the scum of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Seven Warlords are nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna work for the World Government
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or anybody, even if they beg me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Captain Vander Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei is no match for me as \Na pirate in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no match at all, I suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's going on at the harbor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, he said that a \NCelestial Dragon is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like his ship has wrecked \Nand he's asking for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun. Let's go see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't how it was supposed to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! The Fish-Man slaves \Nwent back to their island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it, My Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is the thing, My Son.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Fish-Man named Jimbei just \Njoined the Seven Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Sun Pirates which he belongs \Nto were hiding all those slaves
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but their evasion charges were \Ndropped by the amnesty of the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Government so they went back home, My Son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the slaves who escaped from \Nmy place are among them, My Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me sick to think \Nthat they are living a
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,free and easy life now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go get them back, My Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I've spent a lot of money \Nto collect those Fish-Man slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee! I didn't know that the deep \Nsea was such a horrifying place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:11:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, huh? Myosgard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you address me without my title! Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you were my slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to come home with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't give you my permission \Nto be free, fishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't do it, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Celestial Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you kill him, the \Namnesty will become void!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, fools! Know your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy admirals will come to the aid of a
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Dragon in danger \Nin the world above.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why people are afraid of your folk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're on the Fish-Man \NIsland at the seafloor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as the islanders stay quiet, \Nwhatever happens to you here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll think it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I won't say anything!\N--Me too! Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's barely alive. He's \Ngonna die soon anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him suffer the same \Nway that you slaves did!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Kill him!\N--Make him suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show him no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was a respected man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the life of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Do it!\N--Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid fishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen has been shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, drop your gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Children are watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aladdin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the Celestial Dragon \Nwho's ship was wrecked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got here, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our mother rushed out of the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother-sama, who are the Celestial Dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are humans, Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are quite a few humans out \Nthere and they are the scary ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard some gunshots too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Otohime-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you protect him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know what he did to us in the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He treated us like we were \Nanimals, not even slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel your anguish - it's very painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.01,0:16:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's hard but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can't plant your anger and resentment \Ntoward humans in children's mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They need a chance to meet humans \Nand figure them out on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell the people on the island anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither the tragedy we endured  \Nnor of our anger towards humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Tai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To a Celestial Dragon like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Queen of a fish country \Nis just another commoner...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or even less!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me a mask and a doctor! Otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Sea Kings!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't look like a coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi... Don't tell me you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the family legend, a long \Nlong time ago, there was a Mermaid...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who possessed mysterious power that \Ncould even control the Sea Kings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vander Decken I decided to look into \Nthe legend and headed for the seafloor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ancestors! I finally found her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi is the legendary Mermaid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Don't let anybody hear about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret legend that only \Nmy family knows, I suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can control the Sea Kings as \NI wish, I can do anything I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can have anything I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are we gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kidnap Princess Shirahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.83,0:20:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I have to marry her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's still a kid now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm... that's the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aladdin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me treat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat you next.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A few weeks later,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when the Celestial Dragon \Nwho's life has been saved was
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about to leave for home,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.72,0:20:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime did an unexpected thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get even with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'm a respected \NWorld Noble, you insulted me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and harassed me terribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fishes, I'll make you \Nfeel sorry for what you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what we get for saving his life?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We provided a ship and \Ncrew for him to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could he say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.73,0:21:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't let him go! It's \Ndangerous to this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.76,0:21:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like you have more to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll come with \Nyou to the world above.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the world above?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.71,0:21:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too dangerous, Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.59,0:21:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait-jamon, Otohime! I won't let you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to negotiate \Nwith the Nobles, I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure humans won't catch you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since you're the King and a Great Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.03,0:21:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there is no point if \Nit's a strong man like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to show that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.85,0:21:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even a weak woman can \Ngo there and return home
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.37,0:22:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we want to prove to our nation \Nit's totally safe up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm physically more fragile than \Nanyone - that's why it makes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,more sense for me to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Mother-sama!\N--Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Otohime-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.43,0:22:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.93,0:22:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust the woman who you chose to be your wife
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.88,0:22:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.40,0:22:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just a fish queen - how arrogant!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.43,0:22:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.85,0:22:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.54,0:22:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do is trust her and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:23:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty! Please be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.04,0:23:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime brought a single \Npaper back from the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.03,0:23:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It represents a light of \Nhope for Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.32,0:23:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gathering numerous signatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.15,0:23:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her dream becomes the dream \Nof all of Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish-Man Island seemed ready to change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when all of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.34,0:23:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a gunshot rings out across \Nall of Fish-Man Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Sudden Tragedy! A Gunshot \NShuts Down the Future!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.88,0:23:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
